(558, 1, '2021-12-29 10:23:39', '2021-12-29 10:23:39', 'Go full throttle in the Nike Dunk Low High Retro.It brings motocross-inspired details like bold branding, reflective accents and fresh materials to the wardrobe favourite.Crisp leather, bright panels and flashy details deliver high-octane energy.', 'Nike Drunk High Retro SE', '<b class=\"headline-5\">GET CROSSED WITH OLD-SCHOOL HOOPS.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nGo full throttle in the Nike Dunk Low High Retro.It brings motocross-inspired details like bold branding, reflective accents and fresh materials to the wardrobe favourite.Crisp leather, bright panels and flashy details deliver high-octane energy.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Benefits</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Reflective details, including accents in the laces, for the perfect amount of flash.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bright panels and bold branding (including embroidered \"NIKE\" on the side) celebrate motocross fashion.</li>\r\n 	<li>Crisp leather upper has a slight sheen and ages to soft perfection.</li>\r\n 	<li>Foam midsole offers lightweight, responsive cushioning.</li>\r\n 	<li>Rubber outsole with classic hoops pivot circle adds traction.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Padded, low-cut collar</li>\r\n 	<li>Foam insole</li>\r\n 	<li>Perforations on the toe</li>\r\n 	<li>Rubber outsole</li>\r\n 	<li>Not intended for use as Personal Protective Equipment (PPE)</li>\r\n 	<li>Colour Shown: Black/Black/White/Hyper Royal</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: DD3359-001</li>\r\n 	<li>Country/Region of Origin: Vietnam</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Dunk Origins</b>\r\n\r\nOriginally a classic Nike hoops shoe, the Dunk was organically adopted by skate culture—and in time re-engineered for Nike SB.These days, the SB Dunk doubles as a starting point for many of the brand\'s most influential design collaborators, from small-town skate shops to iconic New York fashion houses.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nike-drunk-high-retro-se', '', '', '2022-01-03 17:03:10', '2022-01-03 17:03:10', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jutta/?post_type=product&#038;p=558', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(559, 1, '2021-12-29 10:23:26', '2021-12-29 10:23:26', '', 'Dunk High', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'dunk-high', '', '', '2021-12-29 10:23:33', '2021-12-29 10:23:33', '', 558, 'http://localhost/jutta/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Dunk-High.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(560, 1, '2021-12-29 10:27:04', '2021-12-29 10:27:04', 'Picture you. Picture you in a tapered, slim-fitting pair of dark-wash jeans. You look dope. And that means you’ll need an equally dope dress shoe. This is where our Brush-Up formals finish the job. Featuring excellent finish and modish design, these shoes are worth investing in which is great in style, functionality &amp; durability at a price that’s impressive. Make sure the length of your pants rests just on the top of the shoe—never let the hem drag on the ground.', 'Caliber Shoes Formal', 'Picture you. Picture you in a tapered, slim-fitting pair of dark-wash jeans. You look dope. And that means you’ll need an equally dope dress shoe. This is where our Brush-Up formals finish the job. Featuring excellent finish and modish design, these shoes are worth investing in which is great in style, functionality &amp; durability at a price that’s impressive. Make sure the length of your pants rests just on the top of the shoe—never let the hem drag on the ground.\r\n\r\nOne pair to slay them all! Whether purposive or not, one’s selection in leather dress shoes can still point the way to a man’s character and portray a lot about his personality i.e. how stylish the man is. Our brush-up formals will provide you a walking experience that’s one of a kind lending a suave look to individuals. Be ready to show-case a refined look at formal gatherings paired with chino pants and crisp subtle shirts.\r\n\r\nBeing dapper comes naturally, with our brush-up formals Formal shoes which are perfect for any corporate gatherings. Crafted from the first-grade microfiber, these brush-ups lend a complete look when teamed with pin-striped shirts, trousers and formal coats. Exuding sartorial elegance coupled by an unparalleled comfort, Caliber Brush-up formals are easy-to-go option at an affordable price.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'caliber-shoes-formal', '', '', '2021-12-29 11:01:38', '2021-12-29 11:01:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jutta/?post_type=product&#038;p=560', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(561, 1, '2021-12-29 10:26:48', '2021-12-29 10:26:48', '', 'Caleber Shoes', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'caleber-shoes', '', '', '2021-12-29 10:26:58', '2021-12-29 10:26:58', '', 560, 'http://localhost/jutta/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Caleber-Shoes.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(562, 1, '2021-12-29 10:32:08', '2021-12-29 10:32:08', 'Picture you. Picture you in a tapered, slim-fitting pair of dark-wash jeans. You look dope. And that means you’ll need an equally dope dress shoe. This is where our Brush-Up formals finish the job. Featuring excellent finish and modish design, these shoes are worth investing in which is great in style, functionality &amp; durability at a price that’s impressive. Make sure the length of your pants rests just on the top of the shoe—never let the hem drag on the ground.', 'Caliber Shoes Formal', '<p>Picture you. Picture you in a tapered, slim-fitting pair of dark-wash jeans. You look dope. And that means you’ll need an equally dope dress shoe. This is where our Brush-Up formals finish the job. Featuring excellent finish and modish design, these shoes are worth investing in which is great in style, functionality &amp; durability at a price that’s impressive.&nbsp;Make sure the length of your pants rests just on the top of the shoe—never let the hem drag on the ground.</p><p>One pair to slay them all! Whether purposive or not, one’s selection in leather dress shoes can still point the way to a man’s character and portray a lot about his personality i.e. how stylish the man is. Our brush-up formals will provide you a walking experience that’s one of a kind lending a suave look to individuals. Be ready to show-case a refined look at formal gatherings paired with chino pants and crisp subtle shirts.</p><p>Being dapper comes naturally, with our brush-up formals Formal shoes which are perfect for any corporate gatherings. Crafted from the first-grade microfiber, these brush-ups lend a complete look when teamed with pin-striped shirts, trousers and formal coats. Exuding sartorial elegance coupled by an unparalleled comfort, Caliber Brush-up formals are easy-to-go option at an affordable price.</p>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '560-autosave-v1', '', '', '2021-12-29 10:32:08', '2021-12-29 10:32:08', '', 560, 'http://localhost/jutta/?p=562', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(563, 1, '2021-12-29 10:32:26', '2021-12-29 10:32:26', '', 'Converse', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'converse', '', '', '2021-12-29 10:32:33', '2021-12-29 10:32:33', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jutta/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Converse.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(564, 1, '2021-12-29 10:34:07', '2021-12-29 10:34:07', 'There’s no need to tie the laces on this slip-on Chuck made for chill days in the sun.', 'Chuck Taylor', '<div class=\"pdp-tab__container  pdp-tab__above-fold\">\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__content-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__content text-align--sm-center\">There’s no need to tie the laces on this slip-on Chuck made for chill days in the sun.</div>\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__list-title text-align--sm-center text--upper text--extrabold body-type--nano\">WHY YOU SHOULD BE DOWN</div>\r\n<ul class=\"pdp-tab__list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Canvas upper is lightweight and durable.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Keep it casual with a slip-on design and fixed no-tie laces.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Elasticized collar for easy on and off.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Medial eyelets enhance airflow.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Standard woven tongue logo.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__container \">\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__content-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab--origin-header pdp-tab__list-title text-align--sm-center text--upper text--extrabold body-type--nano\">CHUCK TAYLOR ALL STAR ORIGINS</div>\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab--origin-collaboration text-align--sm-center\">Created in 1917, the Chuck Taylor All Star sneaker was the original basketball shoe. Its use has changed over the years, but it’s still perfect in its simplicity. With its timeless silhouette, vulcanized rubber sole and unmistakable ankle patch, the Chuck is ready for you to make it your own.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'chuck-taylor', '', '', '2021-12-29 11:01:22', '2021-12-29 11:01:22', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jutta/?post_type=product&#038;p=564', 0, 'product', '', 0),
