(618, 1, '2021-12-29 16:02:02', '2021-12-29 16:02:02', 'Bring the comfort and athletic style of running footwear to your everyday look in these adidas shoes. Step through your day confidently with a snug fit and a lightweight midsole that cushions your feet with every step.', 'Racer TR21', 'Bring the comfort and athletic style of running footwear to your everyday look in these adidas shoes. Step through your day confidently with a snug fit and a lightweight midsole that cushions your feet with every step. This product is made with Primegreen, a series of high-performance recycled materials. 50% of the upper is recycled content. No virgin polyester.\r\n<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\">SPECIFICATIONS</h5>\r\n<div class=\"bullets___NV9iB\">\r\n<ul class=\"gl-list gl-list--s\">\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Lace closure</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Textile upper</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Soft feel</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Cloudfoam midsole</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Textile lining</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"gl-list gl-list--s\">\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Rubber outsole</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Primegreen</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Imported</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Product color: Core Black / Cloud White / Core Black</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'racer-tr21', '', '', '2021-12-29 16:02:02', '2021-12-29 16:02:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jutta/?post_type=product&#038;p=618', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(619, 1, '2021-12-29 16:03:00', '2021-12-29 16:03:00', 'More than just a shoe, it\'s a statement. The adidas Forum hit the scene in \'84 and gained major love on both the hardwood and in the music biz. This pair of the classic shoes brings back the \'80s attitude, the explosive hardwood energy and the iconic removable strap ankle design, distilled into a low top version meant for the streets.', 'Forum Low', 'More than just a shoe, it\'s a statement. The adidas Forum hit the scene in \'84 and gained major love on both the hardwood and in the music biz. This pair of the classic shoes brings back the \'80s attitude, the explosive hardwood energy and the iconic removable strap ankle design, distilled into a low top version meant for the streets.\r\n<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\">SPECIFICATIONS</h5>\r\n<div class=\"bullets___NV9iB\">\r\n<ul class=\"gl-list gl-list--s\">\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Lace closure with removeable strap</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Leather upper</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Rubber outsole</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"gl-list gl-list--s\">\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Imported</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Product color: Cloud White / Cloud White / Core Black</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'forum-low', '', '', '2022-01-03 17:01:43', '2022-01-03 17:01:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jutta/?post_type=product&#038;p=619', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(620, 1, '2021-12-29 16:08:46', '2021-12-29 16:08:46', 'Made with super-soft leather, you can make these as refined or as edgy as you want. You write the story.', 'AllStar Leather', '<div class=\"pdp-tab__container  pdp-tab__above-fold\">\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__content-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__content text-align--sm-center\">Made with super-soft leather, you can make these as refined or as edgy as you want. You write the story.</div>\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__list-title text-align--sm-center text--upper text--extrabold body-type--nano\">WHY YOU SHOULD BE DOWN</div>\r\n<ul class=\"pdp-tab__list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Luxe leather for a smooth look and feel.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Low profile for ultimate flexibility.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Vulcanized rubber soles for increased traction.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Medial eyelets enhance airflow.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Monochromatic license plate.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__container \">\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__content-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab--origin-header pdp-tab__list-title text-align--sm-center text--upper text--extrabold body-type--nano\">CHUCK TAYLOR ALL STAR ORIGINS</div>\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab--origin-collaboration text-align--sm-center\">Created in 1917, the Chuck Taylor All Star sneaker was the original basketball shoe. Its use has changed over the years, but it’s still perfect in its simplicity. With its timeless silhouette, vulcanized rubber sole and unmistakable ankle patch, the Chuck is ready for you to make it your own.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'allstar-leather', '', '', '2021-12-29 16:08:46', '2021-12-29 16:08:46', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jutta/?post_type=product&#038;p=620', 0, 'product', '', 0),
