(625, 1, '2021-12-29 16:09:50', '2021-12-29 16:09:50', 'A style icon for the ages, the Chuck 70 has made a name for itself from the court to the catwalk. This edition stays true to the signature Chuck Taylor look, but with premium details to take your style further. A soft but durable nubuck leather build stands up to wear and tear in easy-to-pair neutrals, while a faux leather ankle patch and waxed cotton laces tie the look together.', 'Nubuck Chuck', '<div class=\"pdp-tab__content text-align--sm-center\">A style icon for the ages, the Chuck 70 has made a name for itself from the court to the catwalk. This edition stays true to the signature Chuck Taylor look, but with premium details to take your style further. A soft but durable nubuck leather build stands up to wear and tear in easy-to-pair neutrals, while a faux leather ankle patch and waxed cotton laces tie the look together.</div>\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__list-title text-align--sm-center text--upper text--extrabold body-type--nano\">WHY YOU SHOULD BE DOWN</div>\r\n<ul class=\"pdp-tab__list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Crafted in nubuck leather for an elevated look and feel.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Premium cushioning for all-day comfort.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Debossed faux leather ankle patch and waxed cotton laces.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Shiny, taller rubber sidewall and winged tongue stitching.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Heritage details like a 1970s heel logo nod to its legacy.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nubuck-chuck', '', '', '2021-12-29 16:12:59', '2021-12-29 16:12:59', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jutta/?post_type=product&#038;p=625', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(626, 1, '2021-12-29 16:10:59', '2021-12-29 16:10:59', 'Running can be as much about comfort as it is about style. These adidas running-inspired shoes have a sculpted Cloudfoam midsole that provides pillow-soft comfort. A knit upper and a bold adidas logo complete the look.', 'Kaptir 2.0', 'Running can be as much about comfort as it is about style. These adidas running-inspired shoes have a sculpted Cloudfoam midsole that provides pillow-soft comfort. A knit upper and a bold adidas logo complete the look.\r\n<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\">SPECIFICATIONS</h5>\r\n<div class=\"bullets___NV9iB\">\r\n<ul class=\"gl-list gl-list--s\">\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Regular fit</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Lace closure</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Knit upper</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Mesh lining</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Heel counter</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"gl-list gl-list--s\">\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Sculpted Cloudfoam midsole</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Synthetic outsole</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Imported</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"gl-vspace-bpall-small\">Product color: Core Black / Core Black / Grey Six</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'kaptir-2-0', '', '', '2021-12-29 16:13:52', '2021-12-29 16:13:52', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jutta/?post_type=product&#038;p=626', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(627, 1, '2021-12-29 16:12:01', '2021-12-29 16:12:01', 'The go-to staple made with super-soft leather, so you can make them as refined or as edgy as you want. You write the story.', 'Chuck Taylor All Star', '<div class=\"pdp-tab__container pdp-tab__above-fold\">\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__content-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__content text-align--sm-center\">The go-to staple made with super-soft leather, so you can make them as refined or as edgy as you want. You write the story.</div>\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__list-title text-align--sm-center text--upper text--extrabold body-type--nano\">WHY YOU SHOULD BE DOWN</div>\r\n<ul class=\"pdp-tab__list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Luxe leather for a smooth look and feel.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">High profile for classic coverage.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Vulcanized rubber sole for increased traction.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Medial eyelets enhance airflow.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"pdp-tab__list-item\">Classic All Star ankle patch.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__container \">\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab__content-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab--origin-header pdp-tab__list-title text-align--sm-center text--upper text--extrabold body-type--nano\">CHUCK TAYLOR ALL STAR ORIGINS</div>\r\n<div class=\"pdp-tab--origin-collaboration text-align--sm-center\">Created in 1917, the Chuck Taylor All Star sneaker was the original basketball shoe. Its use has changed over the years, but it’s still perfect in its simplicity. With its timeless silhouette, vulcanized rubber sole and unmistakable ankle patch, the Chuck is ready for you to make it your own.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'chuck-taylor-all-star', '', '', '2022-01-02 04:37:28', '2022-01-02 04:37:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jutta/?post_type=product&#038;p=627', 0, 'product', '', 0),
